    Verse: 16
Tags:
  - Character
---
The most powerful agent in character-building is the awakening to the true
self, to the fact that man is a spiritual being -- nay, more, that I, this
very eternal I, am a spiritual being, right here and now, at this very moment,
with the God-powers which can be quickly called forth.
